### Store API Tests ###

### Get all stores (public)
GET {{url}}/stores
Accept: application/json


### Get specific store (public)
GET {{url}}/stores/685
Accept: application/json




### Create new store (requires admin)
POST {{url}}/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sallingStoreId": "1234567",
  "name": "Netto Testbutik",
  "brand": {
    "name": "NETTO",
    "displayName": "Netto"
  },
  "address": {
    "addressLine": "Testvej 123",
    "longitude": 12.5683,
    "latitude": 55.7317,
    "postalCode": {
      "postalCode": 2100,
      "city": "København Ø"
    }
  }
}



### Update store (requires admin)
PUT {{url}}/stores/685
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sallingStoreId": "1234567",
  "name": "Netto Testbutik (opdateret)",
  "brand": {
    "name": "NETTO",
    "displayName": "Netto"
  },
  "address": {
    "addressLine": "Testvej 123",
    "longitude": 12.5683,
    "latitude": 55.7317,
    "postalCode": 2100
  }
}

